## 📘 Project Documentation: Voting App for Schools, Organizations & Churches (Final Scope)

---

### 1. 📌 Project Overview

This voting platform allows **schools, churches, and organizations** to conduct transparent elections with rich features like:

* ✅ **User & Subscription Management**
* ✅ **Custom Branding & 2FA**
* ✅ **Device Fingerprinting for Secure Voting**
* ✅ **Live Results & Analytics**
* ✅ **Vote Scheduling & Notifications**
* ✅ **Vote Administration Tools**
* ✅ **Candidate Profiles & Voter Engagement**

---

### 2. 🛠️ Technology Stack

| Layer           | Technology               |
| --------------- | ------------------------ |
| Frontend        | React + TypeScript       |
| Styling         | Tailwind CSS             |
| Backend API     | PHP (Codeigniter preferred)  |
| Database        | MySQL or SQLite      |
| Authentication  | JWT + 2FA (Authenticator)   |
| Payment Gateway | Stripe / Paystack        |
| Device ID       | FingerprintJS / custom   |
| Notification    | Email + SMS (via Twilio) |
| Scheduling      | Codeigniter Scheduler / CRON |
| Charts          | Recharts / Chart.js      |

---

### 3. 🧩 Feature Summary

#### 👤 User & Organization

* Signup/Login + 2FA
* Profile & organization branding
* Subscription: Free / Premium

#### 🗳️ Election Management

* Create/Edit/Delete elections
* **Vote Scheduling** (start & end time)
* **Vote Administration**:

  * Pause/resume elections
  * Close voting manually
  * Monitor election progress
* Set eligibility rules

#### 🔔 Notifications

* **Email & SMS Reminders**:

  * Before voting begins
  * During voting
  * Final voting reminder (1 hr left)
* Confirmation notification after vote
* Admin notifications on election end

#### 🧑‍💼 Candidate Profiles

* Upload photo, manifesto, and bio
* Social media links or contact info
* Shareable profile page
* Voters can browse candidate info before voting

#### 📊 Analytics & Results

* Total voters vs turnout
* Device types, browsers
* Real-time vote count
* Export to CSV / PDF
* Breakdown by candidate, voter location, time of day

#### 🛡️ Security

* Device fingerprinting
* IP logging
* Rate limiting
* JWT + 2FA login protection
* Audit logs

---

### 4. 🔗 Expanded API Endpoints

#### 📅 Vote Scheduling

* `POST /api/elections` (start\_time, end\_time)
* `GET /api/elections/upcoming`
* `POST /api/elections/:id/close`
* `POST /api/elections/:id/pause`

#### 🛠️ Vote Administration

* `POST /api/elections/:id/resume`
* `GET /api/elections/:id/live-status`
* `GET /api/elections/:id/admin-dashboard`

#### 🔔 Notifications

* `POST /api/notifications/send`
* `GET /api/notifications/history`

#### 🧑‍💼 Candidate Profiles

* `POST /api/candidates`
* `PUT /api/candidates/:id`
* `GET /api/elections/:id/candidates`
* `GET /api/candidates/:id`

---

### 5. 🧱 Updated DB Tables

#### `candidate_profiles`

* id
* user\_id
* election\_id
* manifesto
* bio
* image\_url
* social\_links (JSON)

#### `notifications`

* id
* user\_id
* type (email/sms)
* message
* status (sent/pending/failed)
* sent\_at

#### `scheduled_jobs`

* id
* type (reminder, open\_vote, close\_vote)
* election\_id
* scheduled\_for
* status (pending/completed)

